### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los doctores (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener doctor por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo doctor (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Dra. Ana Pineda",
  "especialidad": "Pediátrica",
  "telefono": "3151112222",
  "correo": "ana.pineda@example.com",
  "registro": "RM-2024-010"
}

### Actualizar un doctor (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "especialidad": "MSK (Musculoesquelética)",
  "telefono": "3153334444",
  "correo": "ana.pineda.updated@example.com"
}

### Eliminar un doctor físicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar un doctor lógicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
